title.en: With a Dictionary and No Skirt

description.en: People have always fantasized about that one girl or guy that  you thought you never had a shot with or maybe never even considered.  Whether they're your classmate, next door neighbour, co-worker or even that long time friend you thought was platonic, when that sexual tension reaches a threshold, men and women are unable to resist their basic instinct and procreate.  Especially when it's the first time, things get rough, wild and down right dirty.
